#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.nsmallest.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.nsmallest"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:1 of
msgid "Return the smallest `n` elements."
msgstr "返回最小的 `n` 个元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:3 of
msgid "Return this many ascending sorted values."
msgstr "返回此数量的升序排列值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:5 of
msgid ""
"When there are duplicate values that cannot all fit in a Series of `n` "
"elements:  - ``first`` : return the first `n` occurrences in order     of"
" appearance. - ``last`` : return the last `n` occurrences in reverse     "
"order of appearance. - ``all`` : keep all occurrences. This can result in"
" a Series of     size larger than `n`."
msgstr ""
"当存在重复值且无法全部放入 `n` 个元素的 Series 中时：  - ``first`` : 按"
"出现顺序返回前 `n` 个实例。 - ``last`` : 按出现顺序的逆序返回后 `n` 个"
"实例。 - ``all`` : 保留所有实例。这可能导致 Series 的大小超过 `n`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:5 of
msgid ""
"When there are duplicate values that cannot all fit in a Series of `n` "
"elements:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:8 of
msgid "``first`` : return the first `n` occurrences in order"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:-1 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "return the first"
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:9 of
msgid "of appearance."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:10 of
msgid "``last`` : return the last `n` occurrences in reverse"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:-1 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "return the last"
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:11 of
msgid "order of appearance."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:12 of
msgid "``all``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:-1 of
msgid "keep all occurrences. This can result in a Series of"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:13 of
msgid "size larger than `n`."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:16 of
msgid "The `n` smallest values in the Series, sorted in increasing order."
msgstr "Series 中最小的 `n` 个值，按升序排列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.nlargest`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:22 of
msgid "Get the `n` largest elements."
msgstr "获取最大的 `n` 个元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.sort_values`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:25 of
msgid "Sort Series by values."
msgstr "按值对 Series 进行排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.head`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:28 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows."
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:31 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:32 of
msgid ""
"Faster than ``.sort_values().head(n)`` for small `n` relative to the size"
" of the ``Series`` object."
msgstr ""
"对于相对于 ``Series`` 对象大小较小的 `n`，速度比 ``.sort_values().head(n)"
"`` 更快。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:36 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:57 of
msgid "The `n` smallest elements where ``n=5`` by default."
msgstr "默认情况下 ``n=5`` 时的最小的 `n` 个元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:67 of
msgid ""
"The `n` smallest elements where ``n=3``. Default `keep` value is 'first' "
"so Nauru and Tuvalu will be kept."
msgstr ""
"``n=3`` 时的最小的 `n` 个元素。默认的 `keep` 值为 'first'，因此 Nauru 和 "
"Tuvalu 会被保留。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:76 of
msgid ""
"The `n` smallest elements where ``n=3`` and keeping the last duplicates. "
"Anguilla and Tuvalu will be kept since they are the last with value 11300"
" based on the index order."
msgstr ""
"`n` 个最小元素，其中 ``n=3`` 并保留最后的重复项。安圭拉和图瓦卢将被保留，"
"因为它们在索引顺序中是值为 11300 的最后两个。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.series_nsmallest:86 of
msgid ""
"The `n` smallest elements where ``n=3`` with all duplicates kept. Note "
"that the returned Series has four elements due to the three duplicates."
msgstr ""
"`n` 个最小元素，其中 ``n=3`` 并保留所有重复项。注意返回的 Series 有四个"
"元素，因为有三个重复项。"

